              <div class="jumbotron col-md-12">
                <div class="container">
                  <h1 id="jumbotrontitle">onRouteBC</h1>
                  <p>
                    Permitting and routing for commercial trucking in British&nbsp;Columbia.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row" id="access_row">
              <h2 class="blue-heading-bar">onRouteBC</h2>
              <div class="table-responsive">
                <div class="table featureBoxes-3col">
                  <div class="featureBox col-sm-6">
                    <h3 class="title">Under Construction</h3>
                    <p class="text">Due to unforeseen circumstances, onRouteBC will not be available for online permitting until further notice.
                      The Ministry of Transportation and Infrastructure is committed to providing a system that will simplify
                      permit access and trip planning for the commercial trucking industry in BC. For more information, please
                      contact
                      <a href="mailto:onRouteBC@gov.bc.ca">onRouteBC@gov.bc.ca</a>.
                    </p>
                  </div>

                  <div class="featureBox col-sm-6">
                    <h3 class="title">Commercial Vehicle Permits</h3>
                    <p class="text">For all your commercial vehicle permitting needs in the Province of BC, please contact the Provincial
                      Permit Centre, or use
                      <a href="https://www2.gov.bc.ca/gov/content?id=5D9784357C854A1D92A77F0300D9EF3F" target="_blank">Online Permits</a>.</p>
                    <p>
                      <a class="btn btn-default" href="tel:1-800-559-9688" role="button">Call 1-800-559-9688</a>&nbsp;
                      <a class="btn btn-warning" href="https://www2.gov.bc.ca/gov/content?id=5D9784357C854A1D92A77F0300D9EF3F" target="_blank" role="button">Online Permits »</a>
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

            </div>

