                          <p class="text">
                            6am to 10pm (PST/PDT)
                            <br /> Seven days a week
                          </p>
                          <span style="font-weight: 700;">Hours Exceptions</span>
                          <div id="exceptionPanel">
                            <p class="text">
                              During daylight savings time, the Provincial Permit Centre is open from 5am to 9pm (PST).
                            </p>
                            <p class="text">
                              The Provincial Permit Centre is closed on Christmas Day, Boxing Day, and New Year's Day.
                            </p>
                          </div>
